Description: AdminHelper Agent — FRPC Sync + Monitoring
 Unified agent for AdminHelper. Combines FRP Client
 (frpc) with automatic config sync and system monitoring in a single
 binary. Supports Linux and Windows. Replaces srm-frpc-client,
 srm-monitor-agent, and srm-agent packages.
